{"tid":106508,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[改詞][對地球/人情的最後祝福] 不離不棄 (原曲: 陳奕迅 - 單車)","createTime":"2017-02-03T17:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T15:12:02.000Z","uid":45011,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2922892581fadc58b183e4ef84e5efcf3e1e6c1","tid":106508,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:00:04.000Z","msg":"3度的香港，到處結冰的大帽山上，彷彿歷歷在目，好像大家都從沒有想到，香港唯一一次下雪已是清朝的時候，原來百年過後，差一點就可以歷史重演<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n更想不到的是，這樣一凍，在這一個本來是冬天的日子，冬天就消失了，別說3度，現在13度也很有難度。同時，我們亦不斷受氣候變化的挑戰，除了上天帶給我們的颱風、雨水，還有北方源源不絕的人為空氣污染，讓我們的生活更加嚴峻<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n但是，我們在抱怨冬天還是像夏天的一樣的時候，我們又有否反省過人類是如何破壞地球，現在的一切，不過是地球的自衛還擊? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n然後，我們又有否反省過，身邊重要的人離自己而去，是因為我們親手破壞一段關係?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「為何秋波已盡   才懂得去滋潤」，這句，是你的心聲嗎? <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://aamusictravel.wordpress.com/2017/02/03/%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%9B%E6%9D%B1%E8%A5%BF%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E5%A7%8B%E7%B5%82%E3%80%8A%E4%B8%8D%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%8D%E6%A3%84%E3%80%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamusictravel.wordpress.com%2F2017%2F02%2F03%2F%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BA%259B%25E6%259D%25B1%25E8%25A5%25BF%25EF%25BC%258C%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E5%25A7%258B%25E7%25B5%2582%25E3%2580%258A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%259B%25A2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25A3%2584%25E3%2580%258B%2F&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2F%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=e6a7a1f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://aamusictravel.wordpress.com/2017/02/03/%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%9B%E6%9D%B1%E8%A5%BF%EF%BC%8C%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E5%A7%8B%E7%B5%82%E3%80%8A%E4%B8%8D%E9%9B%A2%E4%B8%8D%E6%A3%84%E3%80%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n《不離不棄》<br />\n原曲: 陳奕迅 &ndash; 單車<br />\n作曲: 柳重言<br />\n填詞: 黃偉文<br />\n改編歌詞: a仔<br />\n<br />\n當你失去清徹的空氣   當你扭轉氣溫亦沒有餘地<br />\n若然花光儲備   能否得到轉機<br />\n<br />\n當雨水已操縱這天氣   當震央已遠超六十八公里<br />\n何事這刻緊靠你   才把我拒諸千里<br />\n<br />\n明明危機   超過生死<br />\n然而誰可   不離不棄<br />\n如何能回復天空當初的美   還有晨曦<br />\n<br />\n明明還可   倚靠雙臂<br />\n然而玄機   不睬不理<br />\n上世紀所開的花早已枯死   何以留低給你<br />\n<br />\n只怪所有天理我不信   只怪反應太少但又太遲鈍<br />\n為何秋波已盡   才懂得去滋潤<br />\n<br />\n只怪不覺得我這麼蠢   只怪將你榨取但又太激進<br />\n何事總得到教訓   才使我覺醒相信<br />\n<br />\n明明危機   超過生死<br />\n然而誰可   不離不棄<br />\n如何能回復冰川當初的美   如何才能承諾給你<br />\n<br />\n我怕過了千禧  沒法子多廝守一世紀<br />\n更怕我是錯在   未秏盡心機<br />\n<br />\n明明危機   超過生死<br />\n然而誰可   不離不棄<br />\n如何從繁盛捉緊當初的你   還有自己<br />\n<br />\n明明還可   倚靠雙臂<br />\n然而玄機   不睬不理<br />\n願我可將畢生青春也交給你   直到你毫無力氣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後記:<br />\n<br />\n呢一首歌未必感夠觸動到每個人既心靈，但如果要揀我最鐘意既改詞作品，呢首一定有份。<br />\n<br />\n「何事這刻緊靠你，才把我拒諸千里」<br />\n曾經，因為激嬲左個自己鐘意既人，但對方Block哂自己所有Contact，自己無辦法搵到佢好好咁解釋清楚，經過數個月醞釀，最終寫左呢首歌。<br />\n<br />\n「只怪所有天理我不信 只怪反應太少但又太遲鈍<br />\n為何秋波已盡 才懂得去滋潤」<br />\n當時，我仍然係一個滿心怒火既少年，把口唔聽話得失過無數咁多人，激嬲佢就係呢個原因，而事前已經好多人叫過我唔好咁對佢，係我唔聽，招致呢個大禍，呢2句，正正係警剔自己，亦警剔讀者們，唔好等到D野失去左至去珍惜，因為，無左，就係無左。<br />\n<br />\n多謝大家花左少少時間睇呢一篇我認為好有意義既歌詞，當然我都希望你地會覺得有意義吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有更多小弟既作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n音樂/旅遊專頁: <a href=\"https://aamusictravel.wordpress.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamusictravel.wordpress.com&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2F%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=d85c827a\" target=\"_blank\">https://aamusictravel.wordpress.com</a><br />\nFacebook Page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/aamusictravel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Faamusictravel%2F&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2F%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=8b35841d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/aamusictravel/</a><br />\nInstagram: aa.music.travel<br />\n<br />\n感謝各位巴絲支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d620d82c7a2420b034bbfb11a8456e19b6dfdb2","tid":106508,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e99a5b752a493c20e6ad4faef66becb7c604785","tid":106508,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T17:29:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁快見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"870c5fcddf4bc8eff0893782027b2d524abe7b06","tid":106508,"uid":26878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T18:41:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f17bc61c0fe310e6abf14a8a6e3e7bd5d93f8d","tid":106508,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T01:36:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aee92e996998a6e91a4ab0ee173c2c5ad6bf442","tid":106508,"uid":35769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ebd2f48d34885845c3a00bc6ad74a0ea64c454","tid":106508,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:41:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6aa4a3ce8b3c8087e5dff2ff854e749337cd4b3b","tid":106508,"uid":47279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612667157b7735a5e47da7af